Full Description: Harris Legal Search is a full-service recruitment firm with an extensive track record of placing singular legal talent throughout the Pacific Northwest and nationwide. We also facilitate the acquisition of law firm practice groups.  Clients range from national and regional law firms and Fortune 500 corporations to private investment, software, and technology startups. Victoria Harris is respected among Northwest companies and law firms as a consummate legal recruiter with an unwavering commitment to long-term relationships, honest communication, and high ethical standards. During a career that has lasted more than 25 years, Ms. Harris has placed hundreds of sought-after attorneys in rewarding positions with companies and law firms. Inti Knapp is a legal recruiter who has placed dozens of attorneys, including general counsel and in-house counsel at companies, and partners and associates at law firms.  Prior to becoming a legal recruiter in 2004, Inti earned her J.D. from the University of Pennsylvania School of Law and practiced litigation at Perkins Coie in Seattle.  In 2015, she joined forces with Victoria Harris, with a shared commitment to ethics and service. A long-standing member of the National Association of Legal Search Consultants (NALSC), the Harris team values the trust placed in them by clients to conduct permanent placement of attorneys in many fields of law.
